OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and sunny start to the
OL,6,Fmorning. A very warm afternoon to
OL,7,Fcome, though the sunshine turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy as the day
OL,9,Fprogresses. An isolated shower may be
OL,10,Fpossible. Breezy, with some mist along
OL,11,Fthe coast at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly dry evening and
OL,14,Fnight with plenty of clear spells.
OL,15,FSome low cloud developing over the
OL,16,Fhills during the early hours. Staying
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
